article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Josh Corbin's 15 points helped Robert Morris defeat IUPUI 92-48 on Thursday night. Corbin added seven rebounds and five assists for the Colonials (5-11, 1-4 Horizon League). Markeese Hastings scored 14 points and added eight rebounds. Alvaro Folgueiras had 12 points and was 5 of 6 shooting (2 for 3 from 3-point range). Justice Williams also had 12. The Jaguars (5-11, 1-4) were led by Vincent Brady II, who recorded 12 points and six rebounds. DJ Jackson added 12 points for IUPUI. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
